modules

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • modules.Module
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArmModule, CompressorModule, DriveModule, ShooterModule

    public class Module
extends Object
implements Runnable
    This class is the super class for all other modules. There are run, start, enable, disable, and reset methods. The run and reset methods can be overwritten by our other modules.
    Author:
    Ben Evans
